description: Health officials say they are "working hard" to identify the source of the infection.
title: Covid-19: Guernsey confirms case with 'unknown source'
title_page: Covid-19: Guernsey confirms case with 'unknown source' - BBC News
maintext: The States of Guernsey said the positive test was returned on Monday evening. Earlier in the day it was announced there were no current known cases in the island.
